    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <div id="instructions">
          <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
              <div class="carousel-item active">
                <h1>How to Add a Bidet:</h1>
                <h4>1. Type in the address of the toilet/bidet in the 'Toilet Location'.</h4>
                <h4>2. Choose Bidet or Toilet accordingly with the 'Toilet Type'.</h4>
                <h4>3. Add an extra details about the Toilet/Bidet (Where it is in the building, A code is needed,
                  etc...).</h4>
                <h4>4. Add a photo of the toilet/bidet.</h4>
                <h4>5. Press Submit.</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <h1>How to Search:</h1>
                <h4>1. Type in any address in the search bar.</h4>
                <h4>2. The map will navigate to the searched address, bidets/toilets near the location will populate
                  the map.</h4>
                <h4>3. Click on a toilet/bidet icon to see relevant info.</h4>
                <h4>4. Click 'Go' to get the fastest route to the toilet/bidet from your current locaiton.</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <h1>How to Create an Account</h1>
                <h4>1. Click the dropdown menu at the top left of the screen.</h4>
                <h4>2. Click 'Create Account'</h4>
                <h4>3. Enter a Username and Password</h4>
                <h4>4. Click 'Create'.</h4>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="prev">
              <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="next">
